===Verb===
{{en-verb|regrett|ing}}

# To [[feel]] [[sorry]] about some [[past]] [[thing]], [[wish]]ing it had [[not]] [[happen]]ed, but something else instead.

====Usage notes====
* This is a [[catenative]] verb that takes the [[gerund]] (the {{term|-ing}} form), except in set phrases with [[tell]], [[say]], and [[inform]], where the '''to infinitive''' is used. See [[Appendix:English catenative verbs]]

